rows.label: tev078101_JNK0010
rows.name: Inquire[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078101_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Atheron about the food situation.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078101_JNK0020
rows.name: Discuss[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078101_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Atheron if anything is troubling him.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078101_MSG0001
rows.name:
My people live by devoltanizing what your people
consider to be toxins. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078101_MSG0002
rows.name:
Consuming anything other than that—your "pizza,"
for example—would be life-threatening to us. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078101_MSG0003
rows.name:
So this integrated production plant of yours is not able
to create the things that we need to survive. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078101_MSG0004
rows.name:
We require chemicals such as the sort that are
produced as byproducts from human weapons
manufacturing. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078101_MSG0005
rows.name:
Fortunately, you humans seem to be especially adept
at creating such things. *fsssh* So I believe we will be
able to carve out a life for ourselves in this city.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078101_MSG0008
rows.name:
*fsssh* While walking through the back alleys,
I encountered a creature coated in sticky black
fluid that was coming from the opposite direction.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078101_MSG0009
rows.name:
It turned out to be Nococche, who was drenched
in voltant for some reason. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078101_MSG0010
rows.name:
The encounter was quite a shock to me. *fsssh*
I quickly heeded my overpowering urge to devoltanize
her with all speed![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078101_MSG0011
rows.name:
The experience left me with a strange affection for her,
and we've been together ever since. *fsssh*
But I still don't understand what happened to her.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078101_SEL1021
rows.name: Ask Atheron about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078101_MSG0016
rows.name:
As long as I have voltant to devoltanize, I'm happy.
I've never had any reason to regret not being able to
eat your human food before. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078101_MSG0017
rows.name:
But lately, watching Nococche happily devour her pizza
has left me with an urge to try it myself. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078101_MSG0018
rows.name:
*fsssh* I know that doing so could be life-threatening,
and I certainly don't want to put anyone through that.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078101_MSG0019
rows.name:
But it would be nice if the folks at Army Pizza would
develop some sort of voltant pizza that my people
could eat. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078101_MSG0012
rows.name:
Nococche has promised to take me on a tour of the
garbage dumps of New LA. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078101_MSG0013
rows.name:
I am quite excited. I hope that they're absolutely
crawling with mold and bacteria! *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078101_MSG0014
rows.name:
It feels as though every day has been more fun than
the last since we arrived in this city. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078101_MSG0015
rows.name:
Many of my kind wish to return to our homeworld,
but I hope to continue my life with Nococche here
for a while longer! *fsssh*[ST:wait ]
